'''罗伯托·阿泽维多'''（{{lang-pt|'''Roberto Azevêdo'''}}，{{IPA-pt|ʁoˈbɛʁtu azeˈvedu}}；{{bd|1957年|10月3日|||df=y}}）是一名[[巴西|巴西]][[外交官|外交官]]，他自2008年起担任巴西驻[[世界贸易组织|世界贸易组织]]大使<ref name= "wto">{{cite web |url=http://www.wto.org/english/news_e/news12_e/biography_robertoazevedo_brazil_e.pdf |title=Biography: Roberto Azevedo |format=PDF |publisher=WTO |accessdate=2013-05-07 |archive-date=2019-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190619191659/https://www.wto.org/english/news_e/news12_e/biography_robertoazevedo_brazil_e.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年5月当选为世贸组织新一任总干事<ref>[http://www.apdnews.com/photo/26193.html 世贸组织正式任命阿泽维多为下任总干事]{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}，亚太日报，2013年5月15日</ref>，并于同年9月1日正式接替[[帕斯卡尔·拉米|帕斯卡尔·拉米]]<ref name="BBC">{{cite news |title= WTO names Roberto Azevedo as new head |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-22443597 |accessdate= 2013-05-07 |newspaper= [[BBC_News_Online|BBC News Online]] |place= [[United_Kingdom|UK]] |date= 7 May 2013 |archive-date= 2017-11-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171127223744/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-22443597 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJAr60 |title=巴西人阿泽维多确定为新任世贸组织总干事人选 |accessdate=2021-11-12}}</ref>。

== 早年 ==
他生于巴西東北部的一座滨海城市、[[巴伊亚州|巴伊亚州]]的首府[[萨尔瓦多_(巴西)|萨尔瓦多]]，曾攻讀[[巴西利亚大学|巴西利亚大学]]的[[电机工程|电机工程]]专业及{{Link-en|里約·布蘭科學院|Rio Branco Institute}}（巴西外交官學院）的[[国际关系|国际关系]]专业。<ref name="wto" />

除了[[葡萄牙语|葡萄牙语]]外，他还能操流利[[英语|英语]]、[[法语|法语]]和[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://covid-19.chinadaily.com.cn/micro-reading/dzh/2013-09-02/content_10015906.html |title=巴西人阿泽维多履新WTO总干事- Micro Reading |accessdate=2021-11-12}}</ref>

==事业==
他于1984年进入巴西外交部门工作，曾先后在{{Link-en|巴西駐美國大使館|Embassy of Brazil, Washington, D.C.}}（1988–91）、巴西駐[[乌拉圭|乌拉圭]]大使館（1992–94）和[[瑞士|瑞士]][[日内瓦|日内瓦]]的巴西常駐代表處（1997–2001）工作。<ref name="wto" />

===世贸总干事===
2013年5月，他在获得[[金砖国家|金砖国家]]以及许多拉丁美洲、亚洲和非洲国家的支持下，赢得159个WTO成员国中的大多数赞成票，战胜了受到[[美国|美国]]和[[欧盟|欧盟]]支持的[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]候选人、当年62岁的[[埃米尼奥·布兰科|埃米尼奥·布兰科]]（Herminio Blanco），成为世贸组织的新一任总干事。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.dayoo.com/world/57402/201305/08/57402_110037152.htm |language= |title=巴西人阿泽维多将成为新世贸总干事 |publisher=大洋网 |date=2013-05-08 |accessdate= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140830113551/http://news.dayoo.com/world/57402/201305/08/57402_110037152.htm |archivedate=2014-08-30 }}</ref><ref name="Guardian1">{{cite web | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/global-development/2013/jan/08/world-trade-organisation-director-general-candidates | title =Ghana gets its claim in early as candidates vie to head WTO | work = The Guardian | date=8 January 2013 | accessdate = 2013-05-08 | last = McClanahan | first = Paige | place = [[United_Kingdom|UK]]}}</ref><ref name="Guardian2">{{cite web | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/global-development/2013/may/08/roberto-azevedo-world-trade-organisation | title = Roberto Azevêdo to be named new World Trade Organisation chief | work = The Guardian | place = UK | date = 8 May 2013 | accessdate = 2013-05-08 | author = McClanahan, Paige | archive-date = 2013-07-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130725234733/http://www.guardian.co.uk/global-development/2013/may/08/roberto-azevedo-world-trade-organisation | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Guardian1" /><ref name= "AlJ1">{{cite web | url= http://www.aljazeera.com/news/americas/2013/05/20135871220756415.html | title = Brazil's Azevedo wins race to head WTO | publisher=Al Jazeera | date = 8 May 2013 | accessdate= 2013-05-08}}</ref>正式选举结果于5月14日的会议上公布<ref name = "wto2">{{cite web | url = http://www.wto.org/english/news_e/news13_e/gc_rpt_08may13_e.htm | title = Troika recommends Carvalho de Azevêdo to be the next WTO Director-General | publisher = WTO | date = 8 May 2013 | accessdate = 2013-05-08 | archive-date = 2019-07-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190725025553/https://www.wto.org/english/news_e/news13_e/gc_rpt_08may13_e.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2020年5月14日，阿澤維多宣布，他将于同年8月31日正式离任，提前一年结束任期<ref>{{cite news |title=详讯：世贸组织总干事阿泽维多宣布将提前离任 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-05/15/c_1125986612.htm}}</ref>。

